    "body": "if I use `unsafe-eval `instead of `unsafe-inline` I get countless errors from all the other scripts.\r\nHow can I solve the problem?\r\nIs there a way to specify `unsafe-eval` only for algolia and `unsafe-inline` for all others?\r\n\r\nSOLVED:\r\n`add_header Content-Security-Policy \"script-src  'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval'   ....`",
